name: ALLAN HOLDSWORTH OVERDRIVE / BOOST
details:
OVERDRIVE / BOOST with EQThe Allan Holdsworth Signature OD/Boost was designed with Allan’s input to create a very versatile tool. This pedal gives you a very mild OD and a very “tweakable” boost section that allows for different EQ emphasis. By hitting the OD with the boost you can get some pretty scorching gain!
